  <summary>A modern cross-platform port of Bermuda Syndrome</summary>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>LicenseRef-Proprietary</project_license>
  <url type="homepage">https://git.yellowkeycard.net/outrider/bermuda</url>
  <url type="vcs-browser">https://git.yellowkeycard.net/outrider/bermuda</url>
  <description>
    <p>This is a re-implementation of the engine used in the game Bermuda Syndrome, developed
      by Century Interactive (now Reakktor Studios) and published by BMG in 1995.</p>
    <p>The modern port was created by Grégory "cyxx" Montoir by reverse engineering the original
      Windows executable and porting it to cross-platform compatible technology such as SDL2.</p>
    <p>The original data files for either the full or demo version of the game are required.</p>
  </description>
